## Base16 Shades of Purple
# Author: Iolar Demartini Junior (http://github.com/demartini) based on Shades of Purple Theme (https://github.com/ahmadawais/shades-of-purple-vscode).
# In file gtk-2.0/gtkrc, delete "gtk-color-scheme" including everything between quotes (don't delete gtk-auto-mnemonics) and inject this.
gtk-color-scheme = "bg_color:#1e1e3f
color0:#1e1e3f
text_color:#c7c7c7
selected_bg_color:#f1d000
selected_fg_color:#c7c7c7
tooltip_bg_color:#1e1e3f
tooltip_fg_color:#c7c7c7
titlebar_bg_color:#1e1e3f
titlebar_fg_color:#c7c7c7
menu_bg_color:#1e1e3f
menu_fg_color:#c7c7c7
link_color:#f1d000"
